OL,3,CRepairs needed on Cregneash cottage
OL,4,Cafter storm damage on the Isle of Man
OL,6,FOne of the Isle of Man's 'most
OL,7,Fsignificant' ancient monuments has
OL,8,Fbeen temporarily closed, after it was
OL,9,Fdamaged during high winds and heavy
OL,10,Frainfall.
OL,12,FHarry Kelly's Cottage is one of only a
OL,13,Fhandful of traditionally thatched
OL,14,Fdwellings on the island, situated in
OL,15,Fthe 19th century folk village,
OL,16,FCregneash.
