OL,3,CRepairs needed on Cregneash cottage
OL,4,Cafter storm damage on the Isle of Man
OL,6,FManx National Heritage has temporarily
OL,7,Fplaced a tarpaulin over the thatched
OL,8,Froof to protect the rare structure
OL,9,Ffrom further deterioration, and to
OL,10,Fsafeguard the cottage's interior.
OL,12,FWork to rethatch the cottage will
OL,13,Fbegin in Spring next year.
OL,15,FThe cottage is named after Harry
OL,16,FKelly, a respected speaker of the Manx
OL,17,Flanguage who died in 1935.
