OL,6,FIt was donated by the Kelly family to
OL,7,Fthe Manx Museum Trustees, and became
OL,8,Fthe first building to open in
OL,9,FCregneash in 1938, which established
OL,10,Fthe village as the first open air folk
OL,11,Fmuseum in the British Isles.
OL,13,FConnie Lovel, Executive Director of
OL,14,FManx National Heritage said: "Harry
OL,15,FKelly's Cottage is one of the Isle of
OL,16,FMan's most iconic historic buildings
OL,17,Fand a cornerstone of Cregneash.
OL,19,F"The damage caused by recent adverse
OL,20,Fweather highlights how vulnerable
OL,21,Fthese rare thatched structures are.
