OL,3,CRepairs needed on Cregneash cottage
OL,4,Cafter storm damage on the Isle of Man
OL,6,F"By acting quickly, we can protect the
OL,7,Fcottage and its interior and prepare
OL,8,Ffor rethatching and conservation
OL,9,Fworks, ensuring this much-loved
OL,10,Fancient monument can continue to be
OL,11,Fenjoyed."
OL,13,FThe full rethatching of Harry Kelly's
OL,14,FCottage is scheduled to be completed
OL,15,Fduring Spring 2026, when visitors will
OL,16,Fhave the opportunity to watch skilled
OL,17,Fcraftsmen rethatching the cottage,
OL,18,Fusing traditional methods to restore
OL,19,Fthis nationally important landmark.
